    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is being sold in poor condition and is recommended for those looking for a major project or a source for parts. The engine struggles with a persistent knock and heavy smoke upon acceleration, indicating the need for a comprehensive rebuild or replacement. Cosmetically, the body shows significant rust on the rocker panels and the interior upholstery is heavily worn and torn. The transmission is also slipping in lower gears, so it will likely need to be towed from the lot. It is sold strictly as-is with no guarantees on mechanical longevity.",
      "price": 6500.0,
